ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectEuropean Space Agency - European Earth Watch Programme ** Arrangement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the ARRANGEMENT between the Government of Canada and the EUROPEAN SPACE AGENCY concerning the Participation of Canada in the EUROPEAN EARTH WATCH PROGRAMME.
